{"tid":1368802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張建宗上台我哋絕對要反，如果唔係我哋就會輸！","createTime":"2019-07-26T14:31:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T14:55:28.000Z","uid":254923,"like":54,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b3b78dff2c54ff0e291c6b0a6ec0fdf028d91145","tid":1368802,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:31:37.000Z","msg":"例如張建宗有可能取代林鄭，你諗下727決戰前夕張建宗密謀取代林鄭咁你都信？<br />\n今日張建宗特登出嚟講溫和嘅嘢，扮退一步，甚至形容白衣人係暴徒襲擊......企圖民意降溫....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中央真係極度陰濕。千祈唔好中計。<br />\n<br />\n溫馨提示，上次凌晨四點開記者會佢已經一粒聲都冇出，仲俾我哋笑係紙版，無論係推送中條例定警察打人睇落去都完全唔關張建宗事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實個局一早已經開始，企圖製造冇殺傷力嘅假象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />由中央推上去代替林鄭。扮係溫和派執政。<br />\n<br />\n我甚至開始懷疑EO表態有機會都係一場Show, 而家已經可以將個故事串連埋一齊....令人感覺政府上下一齊反林鄭，然後順理成章咁樣推（溫和派）張建宗上台，絕對係陷阱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我哋依家要做嘅就係<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">反</span></span>。<br />\n無論中央推咩我哋都反，拒絕接收任何階段性讓步，咁樣我哋先可以保持籌碼談判<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n假設大家真係接受左張建宗，半年之後鋪天蓋地嘅滲透同政策清洗將會全面啟動。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋要盡可能預測中央嘅行動，分析完之後就反，咁就可以儘量止蝕甚至加大籌碼。<br />\n<br />\n不讓步啊，一定要反！<br />\n呢個陷阱好陰險！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24f31119a75debad8f18cd3a58f646281ee14625","tid":1368802,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:33:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a0cba919ee7e3e380d98fb1adf0eaa1c22161516","tid":1368802,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:33:21.000Z","msg":"Push 呢個絕對係陷阱"},{"pid":"b59ab54217cfef5f15c382a518ce065c1e6f6b6d","tid":1368802,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:33:31.000Z","msg":"Push 呢個絕對係陷阱"},{"pid":"fd7451a46ea0eff30eaeaf7e640bd94b3a9ec160","tid":1368802,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:35:45.000Z","msg":"Push 陷阱嚟啊"},{"pid":"c4b55fb43654398549319d8feee675c9908c0a37","tid":1368802,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:35:58.000Z","msg":"Push 陷阱嚟啊"},{"pid":"61ab45fc38bc8d9cbb2be1ba8d30f052b0c0432e","tid":1368802,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:36:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1204ea66d696e47d04b8eca549b40e50213cb817","tid":1368802,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:37:05.000Z","msg":"Push 陷阱嚟啊"},{"pid":"547aac9f3da442da2f53f8e31ba090a1ee97c446","tid":1368802,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:38:14.000Z","msg":"Push 陷阱嚟啊"},{"pid":"a15ee7838cd3e4d1fea5219e99633391d8d7446a","tid":1368802,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:39:02.000Z","msg":"Push 陷阱嚟啊"},{"pid":"404d83c55257c3cc221ba2b141d100e2cec0e7ba","tid":1368802,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:41:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ad4b3d528466bdf6446fa162e8de6f2f4db3a6e2","tid":1368802,"uid":126730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:41:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4a31b293ffbbae5793841782f5e56917c48e7dc","tid":1368802,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:42:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5475a74ea8c5a5d4a0797f90ae3cf71049871e50","tid":1368802,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:42:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a5de419bf95862085fbb337db37bc08ce82a0800","tid":1368802,"uid":166080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:42:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3a9e2f325f9822b9c952a232d17090c2851ce915","tid":1368802,"uid":254923,"lik